WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
The icy winds of Icewind Dale howl through the abandoned settlement of Dougan's Hole.

00:00:03.500 --> 00:00:04.000
[BLANK_AUDIO]

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:08.200
You see strange blue lights dancing in the distance, and the temperature drops even further.

00:00:08.200 --> 00:00:08.800
[AUDIO OUT]

00:00:08.800 --> 00:00:12.400
Roll a Constitution saving throw to resist the supernatural cold.

00:00:15.600 --> 00:00:18.900
The mysterious figure in the black robes turns to face your party.

00:00:21.200 --> 00:00:25.800
"You should not have come here," the figure says in a voice like cracking ice.

00:00:28.100 --> 00:00:32.500
The ground beneath your feet begins to freeze, and ice crystals form in the air around you.

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:39.200
As you approach the ancient ruins, you notice strange symbols carved into the ice.

00:00:42.300 --> 00:00:46.800
Sudenly, a pack of winter wolves emerges from behind the frozen structures.

00:00:49.100 --> 00:00:53.600
The alpha wolf's eyes glow with an unnatural blue light as it snarls at your party.

00:00:56.200 --> 00:01:00.800
Roll for initiative! The battle for survival in the frozen wasteland begins now.

00:01:03.500 --> 00:01:08.100
The temperature continues to drop, and you can see your breath forming ice crystals.

00:01:11.400 --> 00:01:15.900
In the distance, you hear the haunting sound of wind chimes made of bone and ice.

00:01:18.700 --> 00:01:23.200
The mysterious figure raises a staff topped with a glowing blue crystal.

00:01:26.000 --> 00:01:30.500
"The eternal winter has only just begun," the figure cackles with malevolent glee.

00:01:33.800 --> 00:01:38.300
Make a Wisdom saving throw as the figure attempts to freeze your very souls.